{
  "spec": {
    "title": "SHACL 1.2 SPARQL Extensions",
    "url": "https://w3c.github.io/data-shapes/shacl12-sparql/"
  },
  "algorithms": [
    {
      "rationale": "for",
      "steps": [
        {
          "html": "The binding for the variable <code>path</code>, if that is a <a data-cite=\"rdf12-concepts#dfn-iri\" data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/rdf12-concepts/#dfn-iri\">IRI</a>"
        },
        {
          "html": "For results produced by a <a data-cite=\"shacl12-core#dfn-property-shape\" data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/shacl12-core/#dfn-property-shape\">property shape</a>, a <a data-cite=\"shacl12-core#dfn-shacl-property-path\" data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/shacl12-core/#dfn-shacl-property-path\">SHACL property path</a> that is equivalent to the <a data-cite=\"shacl12-core#dfn-value\" data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/shacl12-core/#dfn-value\">value</a> of <code>sh:path</code> of the shape"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "rationale": "for",
      "steps": [
        {
          "html": "The binding for the variable <code>message</code>"
        },
        {
          "html": "For SPARQL-based constraints: The values of <code>sh:message</code> of the <a href=\"https://w3c.github.io/data-shapes/shacl12-sparql/#dfn-sparql-based-constraint\" class=\"internalDFN\" data-link-type=\"dfn\" id=\"ref-for-dfn-sparql-based-constraint-12\">SPARQL-based constraint</a>.\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tFor SPARQL-based constraint components: The values of <code>sh:message</code> of the <a data-cite=\"shacl12-core#dfn-validators\" data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/shacl12-core/#dfn-validators\">validator</a> of the <a href=\"https://w3c.github.io/data-shapes/shacl12-sparql/#dfn-sparql-based-constraint-components\" class=\"internalDFN\" data-link-type=\"dfn\" id=\"ref-for-dfn-sparql-based-constraint-components-2\">SPARQL-based constraint component</a>."
        },
        {
          "html": "For SPARQL-based constraint components: The values of <code>sh:message</code> of the <a href=\"https://w3c.github.io/data-shapes/shacl12-sparql/#dfn-sparql-based-constraint-components\" class=\"internalDFN\" data-link-type=\"dfn\" id=\"ref-for-dfn-sparql-based-constraint-components-3\">SPARQL-based constraint component</a>."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "html": "For every supported shape type (i.e., <a data-cite=\"shacl12-core#dfn-property-shape\" data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/shacl12-core/#dfn-property-shape\">property shape</a> or <a data-cite=\"shacl12-core#dfn-node-shape\" data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/shacl12-core/#dfn-node-shape\">node shape</a>)\n\t\t\t\t\t\tthe constraint component declares a suitable <a data-cite=\"shacl12-core#dfn-validators\" data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/shacl12-core/#dfn-validators\">validator</a>.\n\t\t\t\t\t\tFor a given constraint, a validator is selected from the constraint component using the following rules, in order:",
      "rationale": "for",
      "steps": [
        {
          "html": "For <a data-cite=\"shacl12-core#dfn-node-shape\" data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/shacl12-core/#dfn-node-shape\">node shapes</a>, use one of the values of <code>sh:nodeValidator</code>, if present."
        },
        {
          "html": "For <a data-cite=\"shacl12-core#dfn-property-shape\" data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/shacl12-core/#dfn-property-shape\">property shapes</a>, use one of the values of <code>sh:propertyValidator</code>, if present."
        },
        {
          "html": "Otherwise, use one of the values of <code>sh:validator</code>."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "html": "For each <a href=\"https://w3c.github.io/data-shapes/shacl12-sparql/#dfn-solutions\" class=\"internalDFN\" data-link-type=\"dfn\" id=\"ref-for-dfn-solutions-11\">solution</a> of a <code>SELECT</code> result set, a SHACL processor that supports annotations\n\t\t\t\twalks through the declared result annotations.\n\t\t\t\tThe mapping from result annotations to SPARQL variables uses the following rules:",
      "rationale": "use",
      "steps": [
        {
          "html": "Use the <a data-cite=\"shacl12-core#dfn-value\" data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/shacl12-core/#dfn-value\">value</a> of the property <code>sh:annotationVarName</code>"
        },
        {
          "html": "If no such <a data-cite=\"shacl12-core#dfn-value\" data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/shacl12-core/#dfn-value\">value</a> exists, use the <a href=\"https://w3c.github.io/data-shapes/shacl12-sparql/#dfn-local-names\" class=\"internalDFN\" data-link-type=\"dfn\" id=\"ref-for-dfn-local-names-2\">local name</a> of the <a data-cite=\"shacl12-core#dfn-value\" data-link-type=\"dfn\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/shacl12-core/#dfn-value\">value</a> of <code>sh:annotationProperty</code> \n\t\t\t\tas the variable name."
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}